223
00:17:28,400 --> 00:17:30,164
what will happen to me?

224
00:17:30,228 --> 00:17:32,651
Don't be so superstitious!

225
00:17:32,683 --> 00:17:35,300
You know that's how I am!

226
00:17:35,762 --> 00:17:38,652
Will you help me, Chun-lei?

227
00:17:38,760 --> 00:17:41,240
Do I have a choice? We're best friends.

228
00:17:41,274 --> 00:17:44,778
I'll pretend nothing happened, OK?

229
00:17:44,799 --> 00:17:46,574
Thank you!

230
00:17:48,307 --> 00:17:51,698
Argh!
What is it?

231
00:17:52,760 --> 00:17:53,932
Chatty?

232
00:17:54,306 --> 00:17:55,523
Why didn't you go HP?

233
00:17:55,712 --> 00:17:58,807
We're waiting for you.

234
00:17:59,635 --> 00:18:00,727
Let's go!

235
00:18:08,509 --> 00:18:11,854
Jenny, open UP!

236
00:18:15,761 --> 00:18:17,502
Happy birthday to you,

237
00:18:17,520 --> 00:18:19,443
happy birthday to you,

238
00:18:19,479 --> 00:18:21,652
happy birthday to Jenny,

239
00:18:21,681 --> 00:18:23,729
happy birthday to you!

240
00:18:23,759 --> 00:18:25,523
Thanks!

241
00:18:25,556 --> 00:18:26,728
Make a wish!
Make a wish!

242
00:18:26,759 --> 00:18:30,093
I wish Benny would get run over by a oar.

243
00:18:30,150 --> 00:18:31,447
What?

244
00:18:31,509 --> 00:18:36,936
Benny? Is he the guy from the band
whom you saw kissing your Mom?

245
00:18:36,993 --> 00:18:38,609
What has he done to you?

246
00:18:38,634 --> 00:18:41,296
Whatever it is, you shouldn't curse him.

247
00:18:41,323 --> 00:18:42,575
You'll get retribution.

248
00:18:42,597 --> 00:18:44,087
The creep deserves retribution!

249
00:18:44,121 --> 00:18:46,453
He said he wanted to many my Mom,

250
00:18:46,510 --> 00:18:48,695
but he doesn't want to bring me
with them to the Philippines.

251
00:18:48,721 --> 00:18:51,053
That's terrible!

252
00:18:51,118 --> 00:18:51,778
How can he do that?

253
00:18:51,836 --> 00:18:52,803
If she thinks I'm a burden,

254
00:18:52,868 --> 00:18:54,700
she shouldn't have given birth to me.

255
00:18:54,721 --> 00:18:57,782
I don't know who my real father is.

256
00:18:57,800 --> 00:19:00,497
If she leaves me, what will happen to me?

257
00:19:01,228 --> 00:19:02,696
Don't let your imagination run wild.

258
00:19:02,758 --> 00:19:04,965
Auntie loves you, she won't leave you.

259
00:19:05,634 --> 00:19:07,500
I'm not much better.

260
00:19:07,557 --> 00:19:09,776
As much as my Mom loves my Dad,

261
00:19:09,839 --> 00:19:12,217
she couldn't marry him.

262
00:19:12,239 --> 00:19:15,413
People keeps calling her a tramp,

263
00:19:15,712 --> 00:19:18,568
and they look down on me.

264
00:19:18,596 --> 00:19:21,372
